{"type":"answer","id":133729,"parentType":"question","parentId":15777,"uid":7997,"contents":"事实上除官方语境，墙内是很少会出现“中共”这种称法，而“反中共”、“支持政府”字样一眼便知是反贼作品，恐被当作反向加速。可以考虑更换为更贴合墙内语言风格的文案，比如不传谣不信谣、相信政府相信党等等😏<br>\n<br>\n范例欣赏：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/4xE9l4E.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4xE9l4E.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/4xE9l4E.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-21","agreeCount":43,"discussionCount":0}